5.65pt 1.0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 120%; color: #005583;\">Art. 229; art. 231, &sect; 8&ordm;, I.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm; mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes; margin: 0cm 0cm 5.65pt 1.0cm;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: ClearSans-Bold; mso-fareast-font-family: ClearSans-Bold; mso-bidi-font-family: ClearSans-Bold; color: #005583;\">Observa&ccedil;&atilde;o</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 120%; color: #005583;\">: para tomar posse o Deputado eleito dever&aacute; apresentar o Diploma Original, a Autoriza&ccedil;&atilde;o de Acesso &agrave;s Declara&ccedil;&otilde;es de Ajuste Anual do Imposto de Renda Pessoa F&iacute;sica e a Declara&ccedil;&atilde;o de que n&atilde;o incorre em impedimento estabelecido no art. 54 da Constitui&ccedil;&atilde;o Federal.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),(4,1,3,1,NULL,'Art. 4º','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"color: black;\">No dia 1&ordm; de fevereiro do primeiro ano de cada legislatura, os candidatos diplomados Deputados Federais reunir-se-&atilde;o em sess&atilde;o preparat&oacute;ria, na sede da C&acirc;mara dos Deputados.</span><a style=\"mso-footnote-id: ftn1;\" title=\"\" href=\"file:///C:/Nodejs/projectregimento/regimento-be/RIF-Digital-teste%20(1).docx#_ftn1\" name=\"_ftnref1\"><sup><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"color: #005583;\"><span style=\"mso-special-character: footnote;\"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><sup><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: ClearSans; mso-fareast-font-family: ClearSans; mso-bidi-font-family: ClearSans; color: #005583; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">[1]</span></sup><!--[endif]--></span></span></sup></a><sup><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"color: #005583;\"> e <a style=\"mso-footnote-id: ftn2;\" title=\"\" href=\"file:///C:/Nodejs/projectregimento/regimento-be/RIF-Digital-teste%20(1).docx#_ftn2\" name=\"_ftnref2\"><span style=\"mso-special-character: footnote;\"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><sup><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: ClearSans; mso-fareast-font-family: ClearSans; mso-bidi-font-family: ClearSans; color: #005583; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">[2]</span></sup><!--[endif]--></span></a></span></sup></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 5.65pt 1cm; text-indent: 0cm; border: none; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 120%; color: #005583;\">Art. 2&ordm;, &sect; 2&ordm;; art. 65, I.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 5.65pt 1cm; text-indent: 0cm; border: none; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: ClearSans-Bold; mso-fareast-font-family: ClearSans-Bold; mso-bidi-font-family: ClearSans-Bold; color: #005583;\">Observa&ccedil;&atilde;o</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 120%; color: #005583;\">: a data prevista neste artigo n&atilde;o pode ser transferida para o pr&oacute;ximo dia &uacute;til.</span></p>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><br clear=\"all\" /><hr align=\"left\" size=\"1\" width=\"33%\" /><!--[endif]-->\n<div id=\"ftn1\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm; mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes; margin: 2.85pt 14.15pt .0001pt 14.15pt;\"><a style=\"mso-footnote-id: ftn1;\" title=\"\" href=\"file:///C:/Nodejs/projectregimento/regimento-be/RIF-Digital-teste%20(1).docx#_ftnref1\" name=\"_ftn1\"><sup><span lang=\"EN-GB\"><span style=\"mso-special-character: footnote;\"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><sup><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: ClearSans; mso-fareast-font-family: ClearSans; mso-bidi-font-family: ClearSans; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">[1]</span></sup><!--[endif]--></span></span></sup></a><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 120%; color: #005583;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>CF art. 57, &sect; 4&ordm;. Cada uma das Casas reunir-se-&aacute; em sess&otilde;es preparat&oacute;rias, a partir de 1&ordm; de fevereiro, no primeiro ano da legislatura, para a posse de seus membros e elei&ccedil;&atilde;o das respectivas Mesas, para mandato de 2 (dois) anos, vedada a recondu&ccedil;&atilde;o para o mesmo cargo na elei&ccedil;&atilde;o imediatamente subsequente.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm; mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes; margin: 2.85pt 14.15pt .0001pt 14.15pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 120%; color: #005583;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n</div>\n<div id=\"ftn2\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 2.85pt 14.15pt 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm; border: none; text-align: justify;\"><a style=\"mso-footnote-id: ftn2;\" title=\"\" href=\"file:///C:/Nodejs/projectregimento/regimento-be/RIF-Digital-teste%20(1).docx#_ftnref2\" name=\"_ftn2\"><sup><span lang=\"EN-GB\"><span style=\"mso-special-character: footnote;\"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><sup><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: ClearSans; mso-fareast-font-family: ClearSans; mso-bidi-font-family: ClearSans; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">[2]</span></sup><!--[endif]--></span></span></sup></a><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 120%; color: #005583;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>(<em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">Caput</em> do artigo com reda&ccedil;&atilde;o dada pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 19, de 2012)</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 2.85pt 14.15pt 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm; border: none; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 120%; color: #005583;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>'),(5,1,3,2,NULL,'Art. 5º','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 2.85pt; mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Na segunda sess&atilde;o preparat&oacute;ria da primeira sess&atilde;o legislativa de cada legislatura, no dia 1&ordm; de fevereiro, sempre que poss&iacute;vel sob a dire&ccedil;&atilde;o da Mesa da sess&atilde;o anterior, realizar-se-&aacute; a elei&ccedil;&atilde;o do Presidente, dos demais membros da Mesa e dos Suplentes dos Secret&aacute;rios, para mandato de dois anos, vedada a recondu&ccedil;&atilde;o para o mesmo cargo na elei&ccedil;&atilde;o imediatamente subsequente.</span><a title=\"\" href=\"file:///C:/Nodejs/projectregimento/regimento-be/RIF-Digital-teste%20(1).docx#_ftn1\" name=\"_ftnref1\"><sup><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"color: #005583;\"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><sup><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: ClearSans;\">[1]</span></sup><!--[endif]--></span></sup></a></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<div><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--></div>\n<hr align=\"left\" size=\"1\" width=\"33%\" />\n<div id=\"ftn1\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm; mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes; margin: 2.85pt 14.15pt .0001pt 14.15pt;\"><a title=\"\" href=\"file:///C:/Nodejs/projectregimento/regimento-be/RIF-Digital-teste%20(1).docx#_ftnref1\" name=\"_ftn1\"><sup><span lang=\"EN-GB\"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><sup><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: ClearSans; mso-fareast-font-family: ClearSans; mso-bidi-font-family: ClearSans; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">[1]</span></sup><!--[endif]--></span></sup></a><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 120%; color: #005583;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (<em>Caput</em> do artigo com reda&ccedil;&atilde;o dada pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 19, de 2012).</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm; mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes; margin: 2.85pt 14.15pt .0001pt 14.15pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 120%; color: #005583;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div id=\"ftn2\"></div>\n</div>\n<div><!--[endif]--></div>'),(6,1,3,2,NULL,'Art. 6º ','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 2.85pt; mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">No terceiro ano de cada legislatura, em data e hora previamente designadas pelo Presidente da C&acirc;mara dos Deputados, antes de inaugurada a sess&atilde;o legislativa e sob a dire&ccedil;&atilde;o da Mesa da sess&atilde;o anterior, realizar-se-&aacute; a elei&ccedil;&atilde;o do Presidente, dos demais membros da Mesa e dos Suplentes dos Secret&aacute;rios.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"border: none; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<div><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--></div>\n<hr align=\"left\" size=\"1\" width=\"33%\" />\n<div id=\"ftn1\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm; mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes; margin: 2.85pt 14.15pt .0001pt 14.15pt;\"><a title=\"\" href=\"file:///C:/Nodejs/projectregimento/regimento-be/RIF-Digital-teste%20(1).docx#_ftnref1\" name=\"_ftn1\"><sup><span lang=\"EN-GB\"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><sup><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: ClearSans; mso-fareast-font-family: ClearSans; mso-bidi-font-family: ClearSans; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">[1]</span></sup><!--[endif]--></span></sup></a><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 120%; color: #005583;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (<em>Caput</em> do artigo com reda&ccedil;&atilde;o dada pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 19, de 2012).</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm; mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes; margin: 2.85pt 14.15pt .0001pt 14.15pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 120%; color: #005583;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div id=\"ftn2\"></div>\n</div>\n<div><!--[endif]--></div>'),(7,1,3,2,NULL,'Art. 7º','<p><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: ClearSans;\">A elei&ccedil;&atilde;o dos membros da Mesa far-se-&aacute; em vota&ccedil;&atilde;o por escrut&iacute;nio secreto e pelo sistema eletr&ocirc;nico, exigido maioria absoluta de votos, em primeiro escrut&iacute;nio, maioria simples, em segundo escrut&iacute;nio, presente a maioria absoluta </span><em><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: Sansita; mso-fareast-font-family: Sansita; mso-bidi-font-family: Sansita; color: #005583; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">(257 Deputados) </span></em><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: ClearSans;\">dos Deputados, observadas as seguintes exig&ecirc;ncias e formalidades:</span></p>'),(8,1,3,2,NULL,'Art. 8º','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"color: black;\">Na composi&ccedil;&atilde;o da Mesa ser&aacute; assegurada, tanto quanto poss&iacute;vel, a representa&ccedil;&atilde;o proporcional dos Partidos ou Blocos Parlamentares</span><a style=\"mso-footnote-id: ftn1;\" title=\"\" href=\"file:///C:/Nodejs/projectregimento/regimento-be/RIF-Digital-teste%20(1).docx#_ftn1\" name=\"_ftnref1\"><sup><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"color: #005583;\"><span style=\"mso-special-character: footnote;\"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><sup><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: ClearSans; mso-fareast-font-family: ClearSans; mso-bidi-font-family: ClearSans; color: #005583; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">[1]</span></sup><!--[endif]--></span></span></sup></a><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"color: black;\"> que participem da C&acirc;mara, os quais escolher&atilde;o os respectivos candidatos aos cargos que, de acordo com o mesmo princ&iacute;pio, lhes caiba prover, sem preju&iacute;zo de candidaturas avulsas oriundas das mesmas bancadas, observadas as seguintes regras: </span></p>\n<div style=\"mso-element: footnote-list;\"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><br clear=\"all\" /><hr align=\"left\" size=\"1\" width=\"33%\" /><!--[endif]-->\n<div id=\"ftn1\" style=\"mso-element: footnote;\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm; mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes; margin: 2.85pt 14.15pt .0001pt 14.15pt;\"><a style=\"mso-footnote-id: ftn1;\" title=\"\" href=\"file:///C:/Nodejs/projectregimento/regimento-be/RIF-Digital-teste%20(1).docx#_ftnref1\" name=\"_ftn1\"><sup><span lang=\"EN-GB\"><span style=\"mso-special-character: footnote;\"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><sup><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: ClearSans; mso-fareast-font-family: ClearSans; mso-bidi-font-family: ClearSans; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">[1]</span></sup><!--[endif]--></span></span></sup></a><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 120%; color: #005583;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>CF art. 58, &sect; 1&ordm;. Na constitui&ccedil;&atilde;o das Mesas e de cada Comiss&atilde;o, &eacute; assegurada, tanto quanto poss&iacute;vel, a representa&ccedil;&atilde;o proporcional dos Partidos ou dos Blocos Parlamentares que participam da respectiva Casa.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm; mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes; margin: 2.85pt 14.15pt .0001pt 14.15pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 120%; color: #005583;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>'),(9,1,4,NULL,NULL,'Art. 9º','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"color: black;\">Os Deputados s&atilde;o agrupados por representa&ccedil;&otilde;es partid&aacute;rias ou de Blocos Parlamentares, cabendo-lhes escolher o L&iacute;der quando a representa&ccedil;&atilde;o atender os requisitos estabelecidos no &sect; 3&ordm;</span><a style=\"mso-footnote-id: ftn1;\" title=\"\" href=\"file:///C:/Nodejs/projectregimento/regimento-be/RIF-Digital-teste%20(1).docx#_ftn1\" name=\"_ftnref1\"><sup><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"color: #005583;\"><span style=\"mso-special-character: footnote;\"><!-- [if !supportFo