;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>'),(12,1,4,NULL,NULL,'Art. 11-A. ','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"color: black;\">A Lideran&ccedil;a da Minoria ser&aacute; composta de L&iacute;der e de nove Vice-L&iacute;deres, com as prerrogativas constantes dos incisos I, III e IV do art. 10.</span><a style=\"mso-footnote-id: ftn1;\" title=\"\" href=\"file:///C:/Nodejs/projectregimento/regimento-be/RIF-Digital-teste%20(1).docx#_ftn1\" name=\"_ftnref1\"><sup><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"color: #005583;\"><span style=\"mso-special-character: footnote;\"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><sup><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: ClearSans; mso-fareast-font-family: ClearSans; mso-bidi-font-family: ClearSans; color: #005583; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">[1]</span></sup><!--[endif]--></span></span></sup></a></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm; mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes; margin: 0cm 0cm 5.65pt 1.0cm;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 120%; color: #005583;\">QO</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 120%; color: #005583;\"> 304/2017 &ndash; O Presidente da C&acirc;mara reconheceu a exist&ecirc;ncia da Lideran&ccedil;a da Oposi&ccedil;&atilde;o, e solicitou ao L&iacute;der da Minoria que fizesse a indica&ccedil;&atilde;o do L&iacute;der.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm; mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes; margin: 0cm 0cm 5.65pt 1.0cm;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 120%; color: #005583;\">Pr&aacute;tica:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 120%; color: #005583;\"> L&iacute;deres e Vice-L&iacute;deres da Minoria e da Oposi&ccedil;&atilde;o n&atilde;o podem requerer verifica&ccedil;&atilde;o de vota&ccedil;&atilde;o no Plen&aacute;rio. </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm; mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes; margin: 0cm 0cm 5.65pt 1.0cm;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: ClearSans-Bold; mso-fareast-font-family: ClearSans-Bold; mso-bidi-font-family: ClearSans-Bold; color: #005583;\">Observa&ccedil;&atilde;o:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 120%; color: #005583;\"> o Presidente da C&acirc;mara, em despacho no of&iacute;cio 95/Gab-lid/PT, em 13 de mar&ccedil;o de 2017 criou a lideran&ccedil;a da Oposi&ccedil;&atilde;o e, em 19/4/2017, criou a lideran&ccedil;a da Maioria, com todas as prerrogativas elencadas no art. 10 do RICD.</span></p>\n<div style=\"mso-element: footnote-list;\"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><br clear=\"all\" /><hr align=\"left\" size=\"1\" width=\"33%\" /><!--[endif]-->\n<div id=\"ftn1\" style=\"mso-element: footnote;\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm; mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes; margin: 2.85pt 14.15pt .0001pt 14.15pt;\"><a style=\"mso-footnote-id: ftn1;\" title=\"\" href=\"file:///C:/Nodejs/projectregimento/regimento-be/RIF-Digital-teste%20(1).docx#_ftnref1\" name=\"_ftn1\"><sup><span lang=\"EN-GB\"><span style=\"mso-special-character: footnote;\"><!-- [if !supportFootnotes]--><sup><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: ClearSans; mso-fareast-font-family: ClearSans; mso-bidi-font-family: ClearSans; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: PT-BR; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">[1]</span></sup><!--[endif]--></span></span></sup></a><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 120%; color: #005583;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>(<em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">Caput</em> do artigo acrescido pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 1, de 2011, com reda&ccedil;&atilde;o dada pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 17, de 2016).</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm; mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes; margin: 2.85pt 14.15pt .0001pt 14.15pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 8.0pt; line-height: 120%; color: #005583;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>'),(13,1,5,NULL,NULL,'Art. 12. ','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"color: black;\">As representa&ccedil;&otilde;es de dois ou mais Partidos, por delibera&ccedil;&atilde;o das respectivas bancadas, poder&atilde;o constituir Bloco Parlamentar, sob Lideran&ccedil;a comum.</span></p>'),(14,1,5,NULL,NULL,'Art. 13. ','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Constitui a Maioria o Partido ou Bloco Parlamentar integrado pela maioria absoluta </span><em><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-family: Sansita; mso-fareast-font-family: Sansita; mso-bidi-font-family: Sansita; color: #005583;\">(257 Deputados)</span></em><span lang=\"EN-GB\"> dos membros da Casa, considerando-se Minoria a representa&ccedil;&atilde;o imediatamente inferior que, em rela&ccedil;&atilde;o ao Governo, expresse posi&ccedil;&atilde;o diversa da Maioria.</span></p>'),(15,2,9,3,NULL,'Art. 14. ','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"color: black;\">&Agrave; Mesa, na qualidade de Comiss&atilde;o Diretora, incumbe a dire&ccedil;&atilde;o dos trabalhos legislativos e dos servi&ccedil;os administrativos da C&acirc;mara.</span></p>'),(16,2,9,3,NULL,'Art. 15. ','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">&Agrave; Mesa compete, dentre outras atribui&ccedil;&otilde;es estabelecidas em lei, neste Regimento ou por resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o da C&acirc;mara, ou delas implicitamente resultantes:&nbsp;</span></p>'),(17,2,9,4,NULL,'Art. 16. ','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">O Presidente &eacute; o representante da C&acirc;mara quando ela se pronuncia coletivamente e o supervisor dos seus trabalhos e da sua ordem, nos termos deste Regimento.</span></p>'),(18,2,9,4,NULL,'Art. 17. ','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination: none; border: none; mso-padding-alt: 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt 31.0pt; mso-border-shadow: yes;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">S&atilde;o atribui&ccedil;&otilde;es do Presidente, al&eacute;m das que est&atilde;o expressas neste Regimento, ou decorram da natureza de suas fun&ccedil;&otilde;es e prerrogativas:&nbsp;</span></p>');
